<activity xml:id="act-cuantosVes-imagenes" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Cuántos ves: Dos imágenes</title>

<statement>
  <p>
    <line>¿Cuántos ves?</line>
    <line>¿Cómo lo sabes?, ¿qué ves?</line>
  </p>
  <p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148152">
      <shortdescription>tres puntos</shortdescription>
    </image>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-148153">
      <shortdescription>cuatro puntos</shortdescription>
    </image>
  </p>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++]</p>
  <ul>
    <li>3. I just know it is 3. I counted 1, 2, 3. I saw 2 on the top and 1 more.</li>
    <li>4. There are 2 on the top and 2 on the bottom. I know 2 and 2 is 4. I counted 1, 2, 3, 4. It has 1 more dot than the first image.</li>
  </ul>
</solution>


